data.title: El Paso Symphony Orchestra
data.meta_description: The El Paso Symphony Orchestra's mission is to assure that concert music is made available to entertain and educate the multicultural community of the greater El Paso region.

KEEP THE MUSIC PLAYING!

Donation from our patrons have sustained the day-to-day operations of the El Paso Symphony Orchestra for the past 90 years, from the orchestra scores to the brilliant musicians and guest artists that grace the stage.

E-Newsletter Sign Up

Know before you go! Sign up for our e-newsletter to receive event information and updates.

Latest News

Programs and artists are subject to change without notice. The El Paso Symphony is made possible with the support of the City of El Paso Museums and Cultural Affairs Department, Texas Commission on the Arts and the National Endowment for the Arts.
